phase cml and ph+ all patients for the following reasons: 
 rising % blasts on 2 consecutive haematologic assessments at least one week apart (i.e., from day 15); 
 no complete haematologic response (chr), no evidence of leukaemia (nel), or minor haematologic response (mihr) within 4 weeks;
